  "text": "OpenTelemetry and Jaeger trace context propagation is implemented across Grafana and Prometheus. **Grafana** implements comprehensive trace context propagation at multiple levels:\n\n**Incoming Request Trace Context Extraction:**\n- `pkg/middleware/request_tracing.go:RequestTracing()` extracts trace context from incoming HTTP requests using `otel.GetTextMapPropagator().Extract()` from HeaderCarrier (line 103), supporting W3C Trace Context by default\n- `pkg/apiserver/endpoints/filters/jaeger_tracing.go:WithExtractJaegerTrace()` specifically extracts Jaeger format traces from request headers using `jaegerpropagator.Jaeger{}.Extract()` (line 14)\n- `pkg/apiserver/endpoints/filters/tracing_log.go:spanContextFromHeaders()` extracts span context from headers with fallback to custom \"Grafana-Upstream-Traceparent\" header (lines 37-55)\n- `pkg/apiserver/endpoints/filters/upstream_trace_link.go:WithExtractUpstreamTraceLink()` handles custom upstream traceparent headers (lines 16-24)\n- `pkg/services/grpcserver/interceptors/tracing.go:TracingStreamInterceptor()` extracts gRPC trace context from metadata using `otel.GetTextMapPropagator().Extract()` (line 19)\n\n**Outgoing Request Trace Context Injection:**\n- `pkg/infra/httpclient/httpclientprovider/tracing_middleware.go:TracingMiddleware()` injects trace context into outbound HTTP requests via `tracer.Inject(ctx, req.Header, span)` (line 37), using OpenTelemetry's HTTP transport instrumentation\n- `pkg/services/setting/service.go:settingTracer.Inject()` injects context into HTTP headers using `otel.GetTextMapPropagator().Inject()` (line 43)\n- `pkg/infra/usagestats/service/usage_stats.go:sendUsageStats()` injects trace context for usage stats requests (line 174)\n- `pkg/services/notifications/smtp.go` implements `gomailHeaderCarrier` as a TextMapCarrier (line 207) enabling trace context propagation to SMTP headers via `otel.GetTextMapPropagator().Inject()` (line 116)\n\n**Propagator Configuration:**\n- `pkg/infra/tracing/tracing.go` (lines 281-300) sets up TextMapPropagators supporting both W3C TraceContext and Jaeger formats based on configuration, using `otel.SetTextMapPropagator()` to register the selected propagators globally\n\n**Prometheus** implements trace context propagation for remote storage operations:\n- `storage/remote/client.go:NewReadClient()` and `NewWriteClient()` wrap HTTP clients with `otelhttp.NewTransport()` (lines 161, 223) to automatically propagate trace context to remote storage endpoints\n- `scrape/scrape.go:newScrapeClient()` wraps scrape target HTTP clients with `otelhttp.NewTransport()` (line 2265) with OpenTelemetry httptrace instrumentation\n- `tracing/tracing.go:Manager.Run()` initializes the global TextMapPropagator with W3C TraceContext format using `otel.SetTextMapPropagator()` (line 62)\n\n**Kubernetes** has not implemented OpenTelemetry or Jaeger trace context propagation in the core repository."
}

